name: ꎭ ꂦ ꈤ ꀸ ꍏ ꌩ х ["WEEKLY TIREDNESS" collection]
description: This feeling is painful, but it appears when we feel tiredeness after a hard week. That's why we try not to think about anything. Just want to freeze all. Stop motion. 1 section - 1 day of the week, which contains something. It was. It is. And it will be today. But exhaustion will eat every day, it will be pleasant or not, physical or mental. It is impossible to get out of bed. Monday came ... right on me.  :: Size :: 1700*2000 | 300 dpi :: handwork ::
